sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant QC as QuizController
    participant Q as Question

    B->>QC: POST /quiz/start<br>(category, question_count)
    QC->>Q: fetchQuestions(category, count)
    Q-->>QC: return array of questions
    Note over QC: Redirects to /quiz/start<br>on invalid count<br>or not enough questions
    QC->>Q: beginSession(playerId, category, count)
    Q-->>QC: return sessionId
    QC-->>B: Redirect /quiz/play